{"tid":111990,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"雙子與射手的相愛是定數，也是劫數","createTime":"2017-02-07T20:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T01:03:42.000Z","uid":83034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ab5267bcc31e65ba10539d9284ffc2cef53cf45","tid":111990,"uid":83034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:29:09.000Z","msg":"我同一個射手女拍左兩年拖<br />\n<br />\n雖然間唔中會嘈下，但整體黎講都拍得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暑假既其中一日，我地一大班人去船p，去完之後就例牌食個晚飯啦。全日都好正常，有講有笑，有攬有錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知，個晚返到屋企，佢打電話同我講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係完全無預兆個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢話我係毒撚，同我一齊見唔到我地既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗大家都只係year 2，做下毒撚，打下機有咩唔啱喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n散咗差唔多半年，我到宜家都好掛住佢，成日偷睇佢instagram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢最近好似有新仔......<br />\n<br />\n最近上網見到有人話射手是雙子一見鐘情的星座，他們之間是致命的吸引和致命的排斥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會係咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係上黎呻下，無事我出返去先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1eff2cc22e9c8fc1aa8c179c7abafbe37ed932","tid":111990,"uid":15854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:03:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 半夜訓唔著已經好辛苦 仲要見到依d垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  星你老母座咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾撚大個呀依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25a08b6ff7fd24ff400aa9106c59042093c3507","tid":111990,"uid":83034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:08:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 半夜訓唔著已經好辛苦 仲要見到依d垃圾post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  星你老母座咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾撚大個呀依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d76cfdbeffad6e63f92646cf86c1964aa1d4e74","tid":111990,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:24:45.000Z","msg":"星座撚收皮啦"},{"pid":"10a0c88b35192b1393620c628146d2f299fdd727","tid":111990,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T21:26:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬咁都可以拉到星座事，真係抵飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d3e26343c1ec7f9ca07a784b215c87c93cecc9","tid":111990,"uid":83034,"like":0,"dislike"